               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥaf la-tazkāra madḫane ʿālam “Book for the Commemoration of the
                     Saviour of the World” (fols. 1ra-2vb, 4ra-28rb, 30ra-31vb, 34ra-44vb),
                     incomplete
 I-1) Gadla Takla Māryām “Vita of Takla Māryām (Mäbʿa Ṣǝyon)”
                     (incipit fol. 26ra, explicit fol. 6va)
 I-2) Taʾammǝra Takla Māryām “Miracles
                     of Takla Māryām” (incipit fol. 6va, explicit fol. 28rb)
 II) Malkǝʾa
                     madḫane ʿālam “Image of the Saviour of the World” (fols. 3ra-vb, 28va-29vb,
                     32ra-33vb; incipit fol. 28va, explicit fol. 3vb), incomplete.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- The correct arrangement of the fols. has not been established.</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
