                              fols. 15va, 16ra ዘሚያዝያ: <locus target="#18vb">fol. 18vb</locus> ዘግንቦት:
                                 <locus target="#19vb">fol. 19vb</locus> ተአምር: ዘመስከረም: <locus target="#22ra">fol. 22ra</locus> ተአምር: ዘጥቅምት: <locus target="#22va">fol. 22va</locus> ዘሐምሌ: <locus target="#23vb">fol. 23vb</locus>
                              ዘመስከረም: <locus target="#26r">fol. 26r</locus> ዘታህሳስ: <locus target="#27rb">fol. 27rb</locus> ዘ[n.l.]: <locus target="#30va">fol. 30va</locus> ዘሰኔ: <locus target="#31vb">fol. 31vb</locus>
                              ዘሚያዝያ: <locus target="#37va">fol. 37va</locus> ዘግንቦት: <locus target="#38rb">fol. 38rb</locus> ዘነሐሴ: <locus target="#42ra">fol.
                                 42ra</locus> ዘኅዳር: <locus target="#43rb">fol.
                           43rb</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
