                  <provenance>Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer is mention as the
                     commissioner in the concluding supplication formula on <locus target="#28rb">28rb</locus>. He and his wife Walatta Ṣādǝqān (s. <locus target="#13va">13va</locus>) are also mentioned in the supplication formulas.
 Later
                     on, the names of Walda Māryām and Walatta Māryām have been added interlineally
                     into the supplication formulas, in a secondary hand, in black.</provenance>
               </history>
